trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencyDatabase"></xref> objects.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection> uses the SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection to programmatically access and modify the `databases` element of the `sqlCacheDependency` in the `cache` configuration section.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection>utilizza il SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection per accedere a livello di codice e di modificare il `databases` elemento del `sqlCacheDependency` nel `cache` sezione di configurazione.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection>

trans-unit.source: The SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
